<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The Solusek Champions are in Sol A.  I was with my guild in the bar, and had a few of these pulled to us.  Not sure where they spawn, because we had a 50 pulling =).  The Lambent Sapphire is obtained by giving a Lambent Stone and TWO Sapphires to Gardern in the Temple.  Hope this helps all you bards.  Btw, the Rune does drop off Choon, my group killed him while camping the Ghoul Messenger in WK.<BR>
